{"product_id":"hawkins-universe-aesthetic-sticker-pack-20-pieces","title":"Hawkins Universe Aesthetic Sticker Pack (20 Pieces) | Stickerized","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis 20-piece mixed sticker set brings together the entire Hawkins universe — from cute chibi characters to dark Upside Down designs. Featuring iconic scenes, quotes, symbols, creatures and aesthetic artwork, this collection is perfect for anyone who loves a blend of cute and creepy.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePrinted on premium waterproof vinyl, each sticker has sharp detailing, vibrant colours and a smooth matte finish. They are durable, long-lasting and perfect for laptops, phones, bottles, diaries, notebooks or room décor.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWith 20 unique designs capturing friendship moments, eerie forests, spooky lab entrances, club emblems and fun retro elements, this pack is an ideal choice for fans, collectors and aesthetic sticker lovers.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51001324896552,"sku":null,"price":149.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/StrangerThings20_bb4b1e2b-f26b-4c4e-ba43-73a1520e9e8e.webp?v=1765448015","url":"https:\/\/www.posterized.in\/products\/hawkins-universe-aesthetic-sticker-pack-20-pieces","provider":"Posterized","version":"1.0","type":"link"}